<title>USA: Arnold Industries Q1 shr $0.27 vs $0.19.</title>
<headline>Arnold Industries Q1 shr $0.27 vs $0.19.</headline>
<dateline>LEBANON, Pa. 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>1997			1996</p>
<p> Shr			  $0.27		    $0.19</p>
<p> Net			  7,322		    5,043</p>
<p> Oper revs		 90,539		   82,392</p>
<p> Avg shrs		  26,668		   26,650</p>
<p>(All data above 000s except per share numbers)</p>
<p>Note: The company reported operating income for the quarter of $11.5 million compared to $8.2 million for the same period a year ago.</p>
<p>The company also said it declared a regular quarterly dividend of $0.11 per share, payable June 4, to stockholders of record May 21.</p>
